#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: xml/security_preface.xml:339
msgid "Contrary to popular opinion, there are viruses that run on Linux. However, the viruses that are known were released by their authors as a <emphasis>proof of concept</emphasis> that the technique works as intended. None of these viruses have been spotted <emphasis>in the wild</emphasis> so far."
